      "settings": {
       "html": "<section class=\"wfx-wrap wfx-pad\" style=\"max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 32px 24px\">\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:#6b6557\">/ WHAT I MAKE</div>\n  <h2 class=\"wfx-h2\" style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:40px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:10px 0 32px\">FOUR THINGS, DONE LOUD.</h2>\n  <div class=\"wfx-grid wfx-cols-4\" style=\"gap:20px\"><div style=\"background:#fff;border:3px solid #14110c;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #14110c;padding:22px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:#2b4cff;font-weight:700\">01</div><div style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;margin-top:10px\">Editorial</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a352c;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.45\">Covers, op-eds &amp; feature spreads with a point of view.</div></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border:3px solid #14110c;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #14110c;padding:22px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:#ff5a36;font-weight:700\">02</div><div style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;margin-top:10px\">Characters</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a352c;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.45\">Original casts &amp; mascots for IP, games and brands.</div></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border:3px solid #14110c;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #14110c;padding:22px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:#ffb300;font-weight:700\">03</div><div style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;margin-top:10px\">Brand Art</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a352c;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.45\">Illustration systems that scale across every touchpoint.</div></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border:3px solid #14110c;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #14110c;padding:22px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:#16a06a;font-weight:700\">04</div><div style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;margin-top:10px\">Murals</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a352c;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.45\">Big walls, festival stages &amp; spaces people walk into.</div></div></div>\n</section>"
